=== Combat system description ===

Damage is calculated: skill.damage + weapon.damage

if "elements are aligned" (means that skill.dmg_type and weapon.dmg_type are the same),
damage gets a bonus the size of player.element (or enemy.element)

blocking is calculated:
the element of the blocker that is equivalent to the skill used to attack
For example, player attacks with a metal type skill. Damage = Damage - enemy.metal

If the elements are aligned when attacking, the blocking player elements get realigned.

Player / enemy dies if any elements OR hitpoins reach 0
